text: Jacob Axelsson Lindblom, born 27 July 1746, in Skeda, Sweden, dead 15 February 1819, in Uppsala, Sweden was a Swedish Lutheran clergyman. He served as the Church of Sweden archbishop of Uppsala between 1805-1819. == References == Category:1746 births Category:1819 deaths Category:Archbishops of Uppsala
title: Jacob Axelsson Lindblom
